"The KRONOMETER was written by Elvis Angelaccio &lt;elvis.angelaccio@kde."
"org&gt;."
msgstr ""
"El Kronometer ha estat escrit per l'Elvis Angelaccio &lt;elvis."
"angelaccio@kde.org&gt;."

